				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$a-{\mathrm {\Delta }} D$$\end{document} perturbation (to increase voltage) is applied to D for a positive gradient obtained from the two points.

