				\begin{document}$${\mathrm {\Delta}} D$$\end{document}.
Steady state response: for the proposed MPPC technique, voltage of PV panel equals the voltage corresponding to the MPP of PV panel, i.e., Vm\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
